Name: New Sophiasburgh Coin
Description: A token of multiple uses.
WorldDesc: Simply called "Silver Coins", these coins are a universal currency in New Sophiasburgh. You can use them to buy anything you can afford in Shop.

Name: Defense Points
Description: A Garrison Point's Defense Points. The Garrison Point will be dissolved and the exploration will end once when there are 0 Defense Points.

Name: Development Level
Description: An important indicator of the level of development of a Garrison Point.

Name: Red Multiplier
Description: Increases the Military Development Rate acquisition efficiency during daily result calculation.

Name: Yellow Multiplier
Description: Increases the Economic Development Rate acquisition efficiency during daily result calculation.

Name: Blue Multiplier
Description: Increases the Infrastructure Development Rate acquisition efficiency during daily result calculation.

Name: Red Resources - Permanent
Description: Reusable resources that can be used to increase Military Development Rate during daily result calculation.

Name: Yellow Resources - Permanent
Description: Reusable resources that can be used to increase Economic Development Rate during daily result calculation.

Name: Blue Resources - Permanent
Description: Reusable resources that can be used to increase Infrastructure Development Rate during daily result calculation.

Name: Red Level
Description: Increase the level to activate the corresponding Military Support effects.

Name: Yellow Level
Description: Increase the level to activate the corresponding Economic Support effects.

Name: Blue Level
Description: Increase the level to activate the corresponding Infrastructure Support effects.

Name: Construction Permit
Description: Spend the permit to construct buildings/reconstruct areas.
WorldDesc: The construction permit issued by the Border Commune that allows the holder to construct in the specified area.

Name: Action Point
Description: Resources required to explore an area.

Name: Red Resources
Description: Can be used to increase Military Development Rate during daily result calculation.

Name: Yellow Resources
Description: Can be used to increase Economic Development Rate during daily result calculation.

Name: Blue Resources
Description: Can be used to increase Infrastructure Development Rate during daily result calculation.

Name: Max Blueprints
Description: Increases the maximum Blueprints you can have.

Name: Awaken Points
Description: Tatyana's Awaken Points

Name: Sand Table Reconstruction
Description: Spend 1 Hourglass to perform Sand Table Reconstruction once. Rewinds time back to 3 rounds ago and returns all Action Points spent during that period
